by Shahid Yousuf and Shoaib Malik.<ref>[http://content-uk.cricinfo.com/engvpak/content/squad/257034.html Pakistan One-Day Squad], from Cricinfo, retrieved 24 August 2006</ref> Mohammad Asif and Shoaib Akhtar only played in the ODI series, having returned from injury.\n|}\n| style=\"width:8%\"|\n| style=\"width:46%\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"3\" | England<ref>[http://content-uk.cricinfo.com/engvpak/content/squad/252784.html England Squad \u2013 1st Test], retrieved from Cricinfo 31 July 2006</ref><ref>[http://content-uk.cricinfo.com/engvpak/content/squad/254245.html England Squad \u2013 2nd Test], retrieved from Cricinfo 31 July 2006</ref>\n|-\n! Name\n! style=\"width:20%\"| Style\n! Domestic team\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Andrew Strauss]] [[captain (cricket)|c]] || LHB, [[Fast bowling|LM]] || [[Middlesex County Cricket Club|Middlesex]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Geraint Jones]] [[wicketkeeper|wk]] || RHB || [[Kent County Cricket Club|Kent]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Chris Read]] [[wicketkeeper|wk]] || RHB|| [[Nottinghamshire County Cricket Club|Nottinghamshire]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ian Bell]] || RHB, [[Fast bowling|RM]] || [[Warwickshire County Cricket Club|Warwickshire]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Stuart Broad]] || LHB, [[Fast bowling|RMF]] || [[Leicestershire County Cricket Club|Leicestershire]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Rikki Clarke]] || RHB, [[Fast bowling|RFM]] || [[Surrey County Cricket Club|Surrey]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Paul Collingwood]] || RHB, [[Fast bowling|RM]] || [[Durham County Cricket Club|Durham]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Alastair Cook]] || LHB, [[Slow left arm|SLA]] || [[Essex County Cricket Club|Essex]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Jamie Dalrymple]] || RHB, [[Off break|OB]] || [[Middlesex County Cricket Club|Middlesex]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Darren Gough]] || RHB, [[Fast bowling|RF]] || [[Essex County Cricket Club|Essex]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Steve Harmison]] || RHB, [[Fast bowling|RF]] || [[Durham County Cricket Club|Durham]]\n|- valign