b/20171113200946/http://boxofficeindia.co.in/two-good-2/ |archive-date=13 November 2017 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=11 March 2016 |title= Music Review: 'Kapoor & Sons' |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/music-reviews/Music-Review-Kapoor-Sons/articleshow/51344544.cms |work=The Times of India}}</ref> || Saathi Rey || Arko<ref>{{cite news |date=10 March 2016 |title= Composer Arko Mukherjee raises the pitch with 'Kapoor & Sons' |url=http://thereel.scroll.in/804588/composer-arko-mukherjee-raises-the-pitch-with-kapoor-sons |work=scroll.in}}</ref> \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=2| ''[[Rustom (film)|Rustom]]'' || Tere Sang Yaara || [[Atif Aslam]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lyricsmint.com/2016/07/tere-sang-yaara-lyrics.html|title=TERE SANG YAARA LYRICS \u2013 Rustom {{!}} Atif Aslam|date=6 July 2016|access-date=6 July 2016}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|| Tere Bin Yaara ||rowspan=\"2\"| Arko\n|\n|-\n|| ''[[Baar Baar Dekho (film)|Baar Baar Dekho]]'' || Dariya \n|\n|-\n|| ''[[Tum Bin II]]'' || Dil Nawaziyaan || Arko, [[Payal Dev]] \n|Composed by [[Ankit Tiwari]] \n|-\n|rowspan=\"10\"|2017 || ''[[Laali Ki Shaadi Mein Laaddoo Deewana]]'' || Rishta || Arko, Ankit Tiwari ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"10\"|2017 || ''[[ Faster Fene ]]'' || Fefe Song || Ritesh Deshmukh ||\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=2|''[[Dobaara: See Your Evil]]'' || Kaari Kaari || Arko, [[Asees Kaur]] \n|\n|-\n|| Humdard || Jyotica Tangri\n|\n|-\n|| ''[[Sweetiee Weds NRI]]'' || O Saathiya || [[Armaan Malik]], [[Prakriti Kakar]], Arko \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|''[[Bareilly Ki Barfi]]''\n|Nazm Nazm\n|Arko\n|\n|-\n|Nazm Nazm (2nd Version)\n|[[Ayushmann Khurrana]]\n|\n|-\n|Nazm Nazm (Female Version)\n|[[Sumedha Karmahe]]\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|''[[Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana]]''\n|Jogi\n|[[Yasser Desai (Singer)|Yasser Desai]], [[Aakanksha Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n|Jogi (Male)\n|Shafqat Amanat Ali\n|\n|-\n|Jogi (Female)\n|Akanksha Sharma \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"9\"|2018\n|''[[Hate Story 4]]''\n|Boond Boond\n|Jubin Nautiyal, [[Neeti 